attachments.title: Den Haag - Men's Collared Merino Blend Jersey
attachments.text: Den Haag shows that you can have old school looks with new school materials and styling. A classic looking jersey made in an array of super gorgeous colors, Den Haag will surely have you turning some heads on and off the bike. It's perfect for a commuter or anyone looking to amp up their style quotient on his next ride. For inspiration, we turned to some of the European cycling jerseys once sported by the likes of Coppi and Bartali. In fitting tribute, Den Haag features bold chest stripes (sewn in a manner so as not to chafe while riding)
